docs.abstract: Democratic women are running for Congress in record numbers, and Republican women are trying to match the surge. But retirements may leave G.O.P. ranks depleted.

docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — As female candidates crash the barricades of the Democratic Party and predict a “blue wave” of women in Congress, a string of high-profile departures of prominent Republican women threatens to leave the House with fewer Republican women next year.

headline.print_headline: A Democratic Surge  May Thin G.O.P. Ranks Of Women in Capitol

docs.abstract: Four days into Mrs. Trump’s unusually long recovery period after a kidney procedure, virtually all that has been said is that the first lady is “doing great.”
docs.snippet: Four days into Mrs. Trump’s unusually long recovery period after a kidney procedure, virtually all that has been said is that the first lady is “doing great.”
docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — This week, the first lady, Melania Trump, underwent a procedure for what the White House called a benign kidney condition. Four days into her recovery for the procedure, which experts say typically has a one-day recuperation period, there has been no update on the first lady’s condition.

headline.main: White House Keeps Details of Melania Trump’s Health Under Wraps
headline.print_headline: Postsurgery, First Lady Is Shrouded In Secrecy

docs.abstract: The cases seek a verdict on “post truth” culture and on Mr. Jones, a Trump ally who reaps millions peddling bogus claims about an American tragedy.
docs.snippet: The cases seek a verdict on “post truth” culture and on Mr. Jones, a Trump ally who reaps millions peddling bogus claims about an American tragedy.
docs.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — After the body of Jesse Lewis, age 6, was recovered from his classroom at Sandy Hook Elementary School, his father, Neil Heslin, cradled him for a final time. At the top of Jesse’s forehead was the gunshot wound that ended his life. “It meant a lot to be able to see him,” Mr. Heslin said in an interview. “When he was born, I was the first to see him, and I was the last one to hold him.”

headline.main: Truth in a Post-Truth Era: Sandy Hook Families Sue Alex Jones, Conspiracy Theorist
headline.print_headline: Sandy Hook Suits Target Fabulist And Online ‘Post Truth’ Culture

docs.abstract: Rudolph Giuliani, a member of President Trump’s legal team, said on Fox News on Wednesday that Mr. Trump reimbursed Michael D. Cohen for the payment.
docs.snippet: Rudolph Giuliani, a member of President Trump’s legal team, said on Fox News on Wednesday that Mr. Trump reimbursed Michael D. Cohen for the payment.
docs.lead_paragraph: Rudolph W. Giuliani said on Wednesday that President Trump reimbursed his personal lawyer, Michael D. Cohen, for a payment that Mr. Cohen has said he made to Stephanie Clifford, a pornographic film actress widely known by her stage name, Stormy Daniels. The payment of $130,000 was to keep her from speaking publicly before the 2016 election about an alleged sexual encounter with Mr. Trump.

headline.main: What Giuliani Said About Cohen’s Payment to Stormy Daniels
